9 Sec. 14. (1) The MIDC shall not make a grant under section 13
10 unless the indigent defense system has an approved plan and cost
11 analysis under section 13(4).
12 (2) The first MIDC grant installment to an indigent defense
13 system is 40% of the system's grant award. The 3 subsequent MIDC
14 grant installments are each 20% of the indigent defense system's
15 grant award.
16 (3) After the first grant installment under subsection (2),
17 the 3 subsequent grant installments are based on the MIDC's review
18 and approval of documentation provided to the MIDC by the indigent
19 defense system, including documentation of expenditures and
20 unexpended funds under section 13(14) and (15). The indigent
21 defense system's documented expenditures for the prior quarter must
22 be not less than 25% of the total plan and cost analysis approved
23 under section 13(4).
24 (4) The MIDC may allow an indigent defense system to request
25 to be exempt from the requirements under this section for
26 unforeseeable conditions that may prohibit timely expenditure
27 processing by the system.
